Banking and finanial Domain Study


Intellect Design Arena Products:
Intellect has a full spectrum of banking product under a platform iDigital covering four business lines which are Global Consumer Banking (iGCB), Risk, Treasury and Market (iRTM) and Global Transaction Banking (iGTB) and Insurance. Global COnsumer Banking has digital core(normal global banking), digital lending (for smoothing lending process), digital wealth (for advisors and bankers) and Quantum Central Banking especially for central banks. Risk, Treasury and Market has got tools like OneRisk (for liquidity Risk management), OneTreasury (for management of treasury of provice/state) and OneMarket (for asset management for a organization may be). 


